geolocator = Photon(user_agent="geoapiExercises")
    locator = geolocator.geocode

    map_data = folium.Map()
    for name, location in dic.items():
        if isinstance(location, dict):
            coords = (location['Lat'], location['Lon'])
        else:
            coords = locator(location).latlng
        marker = folium.Marker(coords, popup=name)
        marker.add_to(map_data)

    return map_data
